  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is designed to assess intra-operative procedure outcomes (e.g.,procedure duration)
      and post-operative patient outcomes (e.g., pain)following a modified Ferguson
      hemorrhoidectomy procedure using the Slotted Anoscope with Harmonic or monopolar energy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
